data.title: SBML.org: SBML Level 3 Rendering
data.meta_description: SBML is a representation format, based on XML, for communicating and storing computational models of biological processes. It can represent many different classes of biological phenomena, including metabolic networks, cell signaling pathways, regulatory networks, infectious diseases, and many others.
